<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: Hammerspace -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Cheat_Hammerspace.label>次元空间</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Cheat_Hammerspace.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn’s body compresses its prey down to an incredible degree. You can’t quite tell how many prey has inside this pawn at any given time, though you can guess if you know its limit. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Cheat_Hammerspace.description>这个角色的身体能够将其猎物压缩到不可思议的程度。你无法确切判断这个角色体内此刻有多少猎物，不过如果你知道它的限度的话，你可以猜测。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Cheat_Hammerspace.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Infinite Capacity -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Cheat_InfiniteCapacity.label>无限容量</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Cheat_InfiniteCapacity.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn doesn’t know the meaning of the word “full”. There’s always room for more prey. Always. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Cheat_InfiniteCapacity.description>这个角色不知道"满了"的意思。总是还有更多空间。总是的。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Cheat_InfiniteCapacity.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Belly-clumsy -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_Bad.label>肚皮笨拙</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_Bad.label>
  <!-- EN: this pawn is unsteady with a big belly and prone to tumbling whenever its prey decide to kick around. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_Bad.description>这个角色拖着大肚子不稳定，每当其猎物四处踢动时容易摔倒。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_Bad.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Godlike Agility -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_Godlike.label>神级灵活性</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_Godlike.label>
  <!-- EN: this pawn makes walking around with the weight of multiple full grown people hanging off of its look effortless, in a way that seems to defy the laws of physics. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_Godlike.description>这个角色走路时背着多个成年人的重量看起来毫不费力，以一种似乎违反物理法则的方式。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_Godlike.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Belly-nimble -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_Good.label>肚皮灵巧</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_Good.label>
  <!-- EN: this pawn knows how to keep its balance with a bulging belly. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_Good.description>这个角色知道如何在鼓起的肚子中保持平衡。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_Good.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Belly-functional -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_Normal.label>肚皮功能</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_Normal.label>
  <!-- EN: this pawn is affected by its prey's weight like anyone else. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_Normal.description>这个角色像其他人一样受到猎物重量的影响。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_Normal.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Belly-dysfunctional -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_VeryBad.label>肚皮失能</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_VeryBad.label>
  <!-- EN: this pawn can barely stay on its feet with a big, round belly, let alone jog around. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_VeryBad.description>这个角色拖着大圆肚子几乎无法站立，更不用说四处活动了。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_VeryBad.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Belly acrobat -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_VeryGood.label>肚皮杂技演员</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_VeryGood.label>
  <!-- EN: this pawn moves freely while full of prey, as though its belly wasn't there. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_VeryGood.description>这个角色在被猎物填满时活动自如，就像它的肚子根本不存在一样。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_Mobility_VeryGood.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Tight Belly -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_Bad.label>紧凑的肚子</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_Bad.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn struggles to fit as many prey inside itself as most of its predatory peers can; there's only room for one, maybe (by default). -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_Bad.description>这个角色难以像大多数捕食者同伴那样装下那么多猎物；里面只有一个的空间，最多可能两个（默认情况下）。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_Bad.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Godlike Capacity -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_Godlike.label>神级容量</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_Godlike.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn's skin is supernaturally stretchy, able to expand to sizes that defy all logic and reason. No matter how full This pawn gets, This pawn seemingly always has room for one more. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_Godlike.description>这个角色的皮肤超自然地富有弹性，能够扩张到超越所有逻辑和理由的大小。无论这个角色有多满，似乎总是还能再吞一个。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_Godlike.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Stretchy Belly -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_Good.label>富有弹性的肚子</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_Good.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn can stretch to fit more prey than the average predator. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_Good.description>这个角色能够拉伸以容纳比普通捕食者更多的猎物。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_Good.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Normal Capacity -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_Normal.label>正常容量</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_Normal.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn can fit as many prey as anyone else. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_Normal.description>这个角色能够像其他人一样装下更多猎物。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_Normal.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Claustrophobic Belly -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_VeryBad.label>幽闭恐怖的肚子</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_VeryBad.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn struggles with a lack of capacity for prey. This pawn can't eat prey of the same size (by default), and fills up fast otherwise. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_VeryBad.description>这个角色因为缺乏猎物容量而苦恼。这个角色不能吃与其体型相同的猎物（默认情况下），否则很快就会满。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_VeryBad.description>
  
  <!-- EN: Cavernous Belly -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_VeryGood.label>洞窟般的肚子</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_VeryGood.label>
  <!-- EN: This pawn can stuff itself silly with prey and still have room for more, though even This pawn has limits. -->
  <RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_VeryGood.description>这个角色能够把自己塞得满满的，还能腾出更多空间，不过即使是这个角色也有极限。</RV2_Gene_QuirkForce_StorageCapacity_VeryGood.description>
  
</LanguageData>